      "content": "wait, \"culturally insensitive\"?? lol i assume u meant \"culturally sensitive\" or something, but why would u say to ignore local customs? i thought being sophisticated meant being able to navigate different environments smoothly. also, can u give me more examples of these \"universal\" standards for things like dining or how people should speak in a meeting? like, what's the standard way to conduct yourself?",
